text: Jochen Wolf (26 August 1941 â€“ 2 February 2022) was a German politician. He was a member of the Social Democratic Party of Germany. He was in the Landtag of Brandenburg from 1990 to 1994. Wolf was born in Saxony, Nazi Germany.
